Nodes.Comment: You can [weapon-swap] open the Rocks and Barrels.
Take a Supply with you if you find one. Don't run more Supplies though, focus on Bushes on the way to the Bandit Camp.
You might run into some Bandits around the canyon. If you do, kill them for the nearby Heart.
Only clear Bandits around the POI, you will finish the Heart later at the Inquest base.
Pull the whole base and run inside the building for LoS. AoE everything.
